  <brief_title>Efficacy/Safety of Lansoprazole in Patients With Frequent Nighttime Heartburn</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase III, Multi-center, Randomized, Double-blind, Placebo-controlled, Parallel Group Trial of Fourteen Day Treatment With Lansoprazole 15 mg or 30 mg Once a Day in Frequent Nighttime Heartburn</official_title>
  <sponsors>
